%F A167632 From _Chai Wah Wu_, Jun 16 2026: (Start)
%F A167632 a(n) = 2*a(n-1) - a(n-2) for n > 3.
%F A167632 G.f.: 4*x*(x^2 + 7*x + 1)/(x - 1)^2. (End)
%F A167632 E.g.f.: 4*(9 + 9*exp(x)*(x - 1) + x). - _Stefano Spezia_, Jun 18 2026
%t A167632 LinearRecurrence[{2, -1}, {0, 4, 36, 72}, 50] (* _Paolo Xausa_, Jun 18 2026 *)
